 that reflects the essence of luxury living. With a deep passion for storytelling and an unwavering commitment to quality, our team crafts articles that capture the imagination and inspire our discerning readers.\n\nOur writers bring a diverse range of expertise, covering everything from high-end travel and fashion to wellness, culture, and more. Each piece is thoughtfully created to resonate with our audience, offering insights and perspectives that enrich their lifestyle.\n\n","id":1850260,"avatar-s3-key":"resident\u002F2025-02-06\u002Fk62y3gbr\u002Fresident_logo_black_on_gold.png","twitter-handle":"Resident"}],"metadata":{"card-share":{"shareable":true}}}},{"id":"523ee7af-eec7-4152-bb6b-51707bdc5426","score":null,"type":"story","item":{"headline":["Beatriz de la Cámara The Shape of Silence Collection Walks the Runway with Poise and Precision During Miami Fashion Week"]},"story":{"author-name":"Jeanne-Marie Phillips","tags":[{"id":6596420,"name":"Miami","meta-description":"Discover Miami's unique blend of luxury living, culture, and exclusive events. From upscale real estate to vibrant nightlife, explore everything that makes Miami one of the world’s top destinations.","meta-title":"Miami Luxury Lifestyle: Events, Culture & Real Estate","slug":"miami","tag-type":"Tag"},{"id":6596421,"name":"Events","meta-description":"Stay informed about the latest luxury events, including high-profile galas, fashion shows, and industry gatherings worldwide.","meta-title":"Luxury Events: Exclusive Galas, Shows, and Experiences","slug":"events","tag-type":"Tag"},{"id":6596429,"name":"Fashion","meta-description":"Explore the world of high fashion with trends, designer highlights, and timeless styles for the luxury aficionado.","meta-title":"Luxury Fashion: Trends, Designers, and Iconic Styles","slug":"fashion","tag-type":"Tag"},{"id":6596450,"name":"Fashion week","meta-description":"Get exclusive coverage of Fashion Week events, featuring top designers, iconic runways, and luxury tr