collection-walks-the-runway-with-poise-and-precision-during-miami-fashion-week","author-id":1976375,"access":null,"first-published-at":1781537020784,"hero-image-caption":"Beatriz de la Cámara's The Shape of Silence collection closes the runway at Miami Fashion Week","story-template":"text","created-at":1781298958905,"authors":[{"slug":"jeanne-marie-phillips","social":{"linkedin":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.linkedin.com\u002Fin\u002Fjeannemariephillips\u002F"},"instagram":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.instagram.com\u002Fmedlg_pub\u002F"}},"name":"Jeanne-Marie Phillips","contributor-role":null,"avatar-url":"https:\u002F\u002Fmedia.assettype.com\u002Fresident\u002F2025-02-26\u002F7880asii\u002FJeanne_Phillips_Medlg.jpg","bio":"A recent South Florida transplant, Jeanne Phillips enjoys exploring and sharing her singular insights into the culture and luxury lifestyle of her new locale. Her stories for RESIDENT magazine capture the essence of exclusive local events, entertainment, fine dining, fashion and leisure pursuits from Palm Beach to Miami, along with travel to exotic destinations worldwide. Her writing also brings to life the celebrities and personalities behind South Florida’s most exciting new cultural currents and lifestyle trends. Jeanne Phillips is a seasoned journalist with a strong background in healthcare marketing communications and public relations.","id":1976375,"avatar-s3-key":"resident\u002F2025-02-26\u002F7880asii\u002FJeanne_Phillips_Medlg.jpg","twitter-handle":null}],"metadata":{"card-share":{"shareable":true}}}}]},{"slug":"interviews","associated-metadata":{},"name":"Interviews","type":"collection","template":"section","summary":null,"id":143914,"collection-date":null,"metadata":{"section":[{"id":64247,"name":"Interviews"}]},"automated":true,"collection-cache-keys":["c\u002F5548\u002F143914","sc\u002F5548\u002F64247"],"items":[{"id":"9cff0a58-a51d-4403-b002-4d9a630fbf74","score":null,"type":"story","item":{"headline":["Leading with Purpose: Kylie Schuyler on Global Girls Glow and Why Investing in Girls Changes Everything"]},"story":{"author-name":"Carece Slaughter | Executive Publisher, RESIDENT Media","tags":[{"id":6596432,"name":"Philanthropy","meta-description":"Explore philanthropic initiatives and high-profile charity events making a difference in the luxury world.","meta-title":"Philanthropy in Luxury: Giving Back with Purpose","slug":"philanthropy","tag-type":"Tag"},{"id":6596443,"name":"Global","meta-description":"Explore the world’s finest luxury destinations, cultural highlights, and exclusive experiences. From travel insights to the latest in luxury trends, discover our global perspective on living well.","meta-title":"Global Luxury Lifestyle: Travel, Culture & Exclusive Insights","slug":"global","tag-type":"Tag"},{"id":6596444,"name":"Interviews","meta-description":"Discover exclusive interviews with influential leaders, creatives, and innovators shaping the luxury world.","meta-title":"Exclusive Interviews: Insights from Industry Leaders and Icons","slug":"interviews","tag-type":"Tag"},{"id":6596452,"name":"Business leaders","meta-description":"Meet inspiring business leaders shaping the future of luxury. Gain insights from their stories and achievements.","meta-title":"Inspiring Business Leaders: Success Stories and Insights","slug":"business-leaders","tag-type":"Tag"}],"headline":"Leading with Purpose: Kylie Schuyler on Global Girls Glow and Why Investing in Girls Changes Everything","story-content-id":"9cff0a58-a51d-4403-b002-4d9a630fbf74","slug":"business-leader\u002F2026\u002F05\u002F08\u002Fleading-with-purpose-kylie-schuyler-on-global-girls-glow-and-why-investing-in-girls-changes-everything","last-published-at":1778200219342,"subheadline":"The Psychologist, Advocate, Founder and Executive Chair of Global Girls Glow on mentorship, measurable impact, and the critical window of adolescence","alternative":{},"sections":[{"domain-slug":null,"slug":"business-leader","name":"Business Leader","section-url":"https:\u002F\u002Fresident.com\u002Finterviews\u002Fbusiness-leader","id":64375,"parent-id":64247,"display-name":"Business Leader","collection":{"slug":"business-leader-interviews","name":"Business Leader","id":144086},"data":null},{"domain-slug":null,"slug":"legacy-and-connections","name":"Legacy and Connections","section-url":"https:\u002F\u002Fresident.com\u002Fluxury-lifestyle\u002Flegacy-and-connections","id":64372,"parent-id":64251,"display-name":"Legacy and Connections","collection":{"slug":"legacy-and-connections-luxury-lifestyle","name":"Legacy and Connections","id":144082},"data":null},{"domain-slug":null,"slug":"insights-and-perspectives","name":"Insights and Perspectives","section-url":"https:\u002F\u002Fresident.com\u002Fluxury-lifestyle\u002Finsights-and-perspectives","id":64376,"parent-id":64251,"display-name":"Insights and Perspectives","collection":{"slug":"insights-and-perspectives-luxury-lifestyle","name":"Insights and Perspectives","id":144087},"data":null}],"read-time":8,"hero-image-metadata":{"mime-type":"image\u002Fjpeg","focus-point":[2991,2904],"width":6000,"file-size":5340033,"file-name":"DSC04277.jpg","height":4000},"published-at":1778200219342,"hero-image-alt-text":"A group of women and girls with their hands stacked together in a team gesture","id":"9cff0a58-a51d-4403-b002-4d9a630fbf74","hero-image-s3-key":"resident\u002F2026-05-07\u002Fin4a0b0i\u002FDSC04277.jpg","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fresident.com\u002Fbusiness-leader\u002F2026\u002F05\u002F08\u002Fleading-with-purpose-kylie-schuyler-on-global-girls-glow-and-why-investing-in-girls-changes-everything","author-id":1850274,"access":null,"first-published-at":1778200219342,"hero-image-caption":"Program participants and mentors form a unity circle during a Glow session","story-template":"interview","created-at":1778254100418,"authors":[{"slug":"carece-slaughter","social":{"twitter":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Ftwitter.com\u002Fcarece","handle":"Carece"},"facebook":{"url":"https:\